<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.3.5">
<l>iṉiyār ñāṉaṅkaḷā leṭukka leḻāta ventāy</l>
<l>kaṉivār vīṭṭiṉpa mēyeṉ kaṭaṟpaṭā vamutē</l>
<l>taṉiyēṉ vāḻmutalē poḻilēḻu mēṉa moṉṟāy</l>
<l>nuṉiyār kōṭṭil vaittā yuṉpātañ cērntēṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Now who [is there] to weigh [you] by cognitions, my father who does not rise?</l>
<l>Pleasure of liberation, full of compassion, ambrosia that did not touch the sea,</l>
<l>living basis of solitary me – I joined the feet of you who as a boar</l>
<l>placed on [you] pointed tusk all the seven groves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
